{"tid":1829314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"翻查資料沙士於2003年2月21日傳入香港","createTime":"2020-01-18T15:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T22:39:14.000Z","uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef79616f93161b338189c76d966d5c8aa0413c8","tid":1829314,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T15:24:16.000Z","msg":"翻查資料，沙士於2003年2月21日傳入香港，當時一名染病的廣州中山大學退休教授來港，並入住旺角一間酒店；至3月初時，沙田威爾斯親王醫院大批醫護人員被證實染上疫症。<br />\n<br />\n相比起股市在疫情過後的迅速回升，沙士「後遺症」對樓市困擾更深。2003年7月，「沙士重災區」淘大花園錄得一宗低價成交，該屋苑L座低層4號室以55萬元售出，實用呎價僅約1708元；建築呎價約1242元。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日，恒指約二萬八千點，即自沙士以來升幅約兩倍多；而淘大花園的呎價已飈升至1.6萬元以上，升幅達8倍以上，反映出這些年來樓市已跑贏了股市。"},{"pid":"f92ac16b485c0e888ac820dc61ec28a0cfe7cb5e","tid":1829314,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T00:52:48.000Z","msg":"估下武漢肺炎最快幾時入黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b4ac9c5361707f670f276fcb54abbb5bee08c3","tid":1829314,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T22:10:58.000Z","msg":"各位，珍惜健康的日子"},{"pid":"9c4bb262c50c040b1cbc6a578e3502cb26f22706","tid":1829314,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T22:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnUtdO6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnUtdO6.png&h=0f38f193&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnohRAM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnohRAM.png&h=f26200cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0O5L0uc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0O5L0uc.png&h=c573d52a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ezpg69j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzpg69j.png&h=96630532&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}